4. Tensor / Pattern Layer

The real upgrade is not the markers. It’s the delta field.

ETI tensor concept

Let each body zone be a coordinate and each state type be a channel.

T[z, c, t]

Where:
	•	z = zone
	•	c = channel such as pain, stress, energy
	•	t = time

This gives you:
	•	clustering
	•	trend detection
	•	anomaly detection
	•	cross-channel correlation

Example

T[neck, pain, t] = 7
T[chest, stress, t] = 4
T[global, sleep, t] = 3

Then derive:

delta = T[..., t] - T[..., t-1]

That becomes your Pattern Engine fuel.

